posts.post_title: WTT for T206s - Various material, cards, autographs, postcards
posts.post_content: Looking to trade for T206s graded in PSA/SCG 4/5 - I have various collectibles located in my Net54 TRADE Folder which are available. (I'm not interested in trading from the other folders) Would especially like to find some of the rarer non Hall of Famers and also Boston players but willing to consider any needed cards.  My collection currently only has about 150 different so there are many options, thank you.  Jim
